This brings up what was, to me, the most shocking part of the earnings call=
; I don=E2=80=99t normally pick on analysts, but this question baffled me:

Mark, this one=E2=80=99s a bit more philosophical, but if we compare where =
Meta is today kind of pre IDFA cookie deprecation type of world, how do you=
